          <description><![CDATA[<p><strong><span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px;">Caracter&iacute;sticas</span></span></strong></p>

<ul>
	<li><span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">Energ&iacute;a lum&iacute;nica.</span></span></li>
</ul>

<ul>
	<li><span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">Energ&iacute;a calor&iacute;fica.</span></span></li>
</ul>

<ul>
	<li><span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">Proviene del Sol.</span></span></li>
</ul>

<ul>
	<li><span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">Llega a la Tierra en forma de radiaci&oacute;n solar.</span></span></li>
</ul>

<ul>
	<li><span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">Es renovable.</span></span></li>
</ul>
]]></description>
